{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy/issues/339","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy/issues/339/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy/issues/339/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy/issues/339/events","html_url":"https://github.com/allenai/scispacy/issues/339","id":834753747,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU4MzQ3NTM3NDc=","number":339,"title":"Potential IndexError in hyponym_detector.py","user":{"login":"astraszab","id":40484210,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQwNDg0MjEw","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/40484210?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab","html_url":"https://github.com/astraszab","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/astraszab/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2021-03-18T12:38:22Z","updated_at":"2021-03-19T17:27:15Z","closed_at":"2021-03-19T17:27:15Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"I've noticed there's potentially unbounded index increment/decrement inside while cycles of the expand_to_noun_compound  method of [HyponymDetector](https://github.com/allenai/scispacy/blob/master/scispacy/hyponym_detector.py). Also I believe the variable name inside the second cycle should be next, not previous\r\n\r\n```\r\ndef expand_to_noun_compound(self, token: Token, doc: Doc):\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n        Expand a token to it's noun phrase based\r\n        on a simple POS tag heuristic.\r\n        \"\"\"\r\n\r\n        start = token.i\r\n        while True:\r\n            previous = doc[start - 1]\r\n            if previous.pos_ in {\"PROPN\", \"NOUN\", \"PRON\"}:\r\n                start -= 1\r\n            else:\r\n                break\r\n\r\n        end = token.i + 1\r\n        while True:\r\n            previous = doc[end]\r\n            if previous.pos_ in {\"PROPN\", \"NOUN\", \"PRON\"}:\r\n                end += 1\r\n            else:\r\n                break\r\n```","closed_by":{"login":"dakinggg","id":43149077,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzMTQ5MDc3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43149077?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg","html_url":"https://github.com/dakinggg","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dakinggg/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy/issues/339/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/allenai/scispacy/issues/339/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"com